    </div>

    <div class="hero-slide"
        style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523580846011-d3a5bc25702b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=80');">
    </div>


    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>

    <div class="hero-content">
        <h1>Empowering Students to Succeed</h1>
        <p>
            Smart Academy provides high-quality education programs designed
            to build confidence, communication skills, and academic excellence
